@startuml
' Sequence: user views movie detail, app fetches TMDB and server comments/ratings
actor User
participant Browser
participant "MoviesDetailPage (React)" as Page
participant "TMDB API" as TMDB
participant "Server: Comments API" as Comments
participant "Server: Ratings API" as Ratings

User -> Browser : click movie card
Browser -> Page : navigate /movies/:id (render)
Page -> TMDB : GET /movie/:id (details)
TMDB --> Page : 200 OK (movie details)
Page -> TMDB : GET /movie/:id/credits
TMDB --> Page : 200 OK (credits)
Page -> Comments : GET /comments?movieId=:id
Comments --> Page : 200 OK (comments[])
Page -> Ratings : GET /ratings?movieId=:id
Ratings --> Page : 200 OK (ratings summary)
Page -> Browser : render movie details + cast + comments + rating UI

' user posts comment
User -> Browser : submit comment
Browser -> Page : POST /comments {movieId, text}
Page -> Comments : POST /comments {movieId, text, user}
Comments --> Page : 201 Created (comment)
Page -> Browser : append comment to UI

' user rates
User -> Browser : submit rating
Browser -> Page : POST /ratings {movieId, rating}
Page -> Ratings : POST /ratings {movieId, rating, user}
Ratings --> Page : 201 Created (rating)
Page -> Browser : update rating UI

@enduml
